														</div>
			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-2789848">
									

<p>It's hard for me to sympathize with the Circus. It's basically Icky and co. blowing up some innocent schmuck who's part of the GOC. Reminds me of informants in Afghanistan who would be murdered by insurgents. If anything, I want to see the Circus suffer a swift, painful comeuppance at the hands of a Strike Force or three.</p>

