														</div>
			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-2790048">
									

<p>Ehhhh, I'm not very fond of how the Circus is portrayed here. I've written quite a bit of Circus stuff myself and talked with Peppersghost about the Circus' past, and if anything Herman himself was an asshole while Manny actually made things a lot better. Also, I've always believed the Circus isn't the stereotypical evil chopper carnival but an actual entertainment group with <em>(admittedly)</em> a lot of weird stuff, who actually want to give people a good time. Sorry, but -1 from me; I like Circus stuff, but I don't like this portrayal of them.</p>

							</div>

								
					
