<p>I was not surprised by Jerry getting pinata'd to death. The GOC doesn't have a good track record from the POV of someone like Icky. I don't think an Essie P Agent would have been killed, although a brutal ejection would certainly have occurred. The Circus has never struck me as being warm and welcoming to normies - it's a twisted sanctuary for twisted anomalies. Turning prepubescent runaways into circus freaks with Clown Milk is not an objectively good act.</p>
<p>Victor is probably wondering if MC&amp;D would be willing to reassign him to somewhere less disquieting.</p>

