<p>I would of liked to see something more horrific happen. Like the candy excrement being reformed into the former GOI member and then him having to serve the circus as a shit monster&#8230; or maybe a fun lover&#8230; Something that both tortures and submits to servitude. Because sometimes death is too good for some folks.</p>

							</div>

								
					
